'''顯微鏡下多血管炎'''({{lang|en|Microscopic polyangiitis}}、也稱為"微觀多動脈炎"(Microscopic polyarteritis)，<ref name="Bolognia" />"微觀多動脈炎結節(Microscopic polyarteritis nodosa)，<ref name="Bolognia">{{cite book
 |author=Rapini, Ronald P.; Bolognia, Jean L.; Jorizzo, Joseph L. |isbn=1-4160-2999-0 
 |title=Dermatology: 2-Volume Set |publisher=Mosby |location=St. Louis |year=2007 }}</ref>'''{{lang|en|MPA}}'''<ref name=FDA20110419>{{cite press release |title=FDA approves Rituxan to treat two rare disorders |publisher=[[Food_and_Drug_Administration|Food and Drug Administration]] |url=http://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/ucm251946.htm |accessdate=20 April 2011 |date=19 April 2011 |archive-date=2017-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118091140/http://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/ucm251946.htm |dead-url=no }}<br/>{{cite web |title=RITUXAN (rituximab) injection, solution |work=Daily Med |publisher=U.S. National Library of Medicine |url=http://dailymed.nlm.nih.gov/dailymed/lookup.cfm?setid=b172773b-3905-4a1c-ad95-bab4b6126563 }}</ref>)是一個不明確的[[自體免疫性疾病|自體免疫性疾病]]，其特徵是全身性的、[[微量免疫|微量免疫]](Pauci-immune/寡免疫)、壞死性、小[[血管炎|血管炎]]而無壞死性[[肉芽腫|肉芽腫]](Granuloma)[[炎症|炎症]]的臨床或病理證據。

==病情==
{{seealso|腎功能|腎生理學}}

臨床特徵包括全身症狀，如發熱、厭食、消瘦、乏力，和腎功能衰竭。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Altaie R, Ditizio F, Fahy GT |title=Microscopic polyangitis presenting with sub-acute reversible optic neuropathy |journal=Eye (Lond) |volume=19 |issue=3 |pages=363–5 |date=March 2005 |pmid=15272290 |doi=10.1038/sj.eye.6701479 }}</ref>多數患者可有[[血尿|血尿]]和[[蛋白尿|蛋白尿]]。[[急进性肾小球肾炎|急进性肾小球肾炎]]很快可能會出現。因為許多不同的器官系統可能參與其中，在MPA可能有廣泛範圍的症狀。

[[紫癜|紫癜]]和[[青斑|青斑]]可以存在。<ref name="pmid19059827">{{cite journal |author=Nagai Y, Hasegawa M, Igarashi N, Tanaka S, Yamanaka M, Ishikawa O |title=Cutaneous manifestations and histological features of microscopic polyangiitis |journal=Eur J Dermatol |volume= 19|issue= 1|pages= 57–60|date=December 2008 |pmid=19059827 |doi=10.1684/ejd.2008.0566 }}</ref>

==診斷==<!--
Laboratory tests may reveal an increased [[sedimentation_rate|sedimentation rate]], elevated [[CRP|CRP]], [[anemia|anemia]] and elevated creatinine due to renal impairment. An important diagnostic test is the presence of [[perinuclear_antineutrophil_cytoplasmic_antibodies|perinuclear antineutrophil cytoplasmic antibodies]] (p-ANCA) with [[myeloperoxidase|myeloperoxidase]] specificity<ref name="pmid15319159">{{cite journal |author=Seishima M, Oyama Z, Oda M |title=Skin eruptions associated with microscopic polyangiitis |journal=Eur J Dermatol |volume=14 |issue=4 |pages=255–8 |year=2004 |pmid=15319159 |url=http://www.john-libbey-eurotext.fr/medline.md?issn=1167-1122&vol=14&iss=4&page=255}}</ref> (a constituent of [[neutrophil|neutrophil]] granules), and [[protein|protein]] and red blood cells in the [[urine|urine]]. -->

患者的神經病變，由"肌電圖"(EMG)可顯示出一種"感覺運動性周圍神經病"(sensorimotor peripheral neuropathy)。

